<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Szerverhiba | NetMafia</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #8B0000;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 100px;
            color: #8B0000;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            margin: 0;
        }
        .error-title {
            color: #aa0000;
            font-family: 'Impact', sans-serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ccc;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .debug-info {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #aa0000, #880000);
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid #660000;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-code">💥 500</div>
        
        <h1 class="error-title">Valami NAGYON elromlott!</h1>
        
        <p class="error-message">
            A szerver éppen bajban van. A főnök már dolgozik a megoldáson! 🔧
        </p>

        {% if debug and message %}
        <div class="debug-info">
            <strong style="color: #fff;">Hiba:</strong><br>
            {{ message }}
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div>
            <a href="/game" class="btn btn-primary">← Vissza a játékba</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
